./vplay -h
usage: vplay [-h] --saal SAAL --type {cam,recording,stream,loudness} [--option {0,1,2,3,4,5}]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --saal SAAL, -s SAAL  saal to select
  --type {cam,recording,stream,loudness}, -t {cam,recording,stream,loudness}
                        what to play
  --option {0,1,2,3,4,5}, -o {0,1,2,3,4,5}
                        which cam (1 to 5)
                        or stream (1=hls hd, 2=hls sd, 3=webm hd, 4=webm sd, 5 slides)
                        or audio source (0=native, 1=translated 1, 2=translated 2) to play
